==Month of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЬИ)==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Kou|ja|зФ≤|1=Kinoe (зФ≤)}} and {{ill|Ki|ja|еЈ±|1=Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11жЬИ}} is designated as the Besshi {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жЬИ}}. However, the term "month" here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Daisetsu|ja|е§ІйЫ™}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|е∞ПеѓТ}}) as applicable.

