==Month of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЬИ)==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Kou|ja|зФ≤|1=Kinoe (зФ≤)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Ki|ja|еЈ±|1=Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11жЬИ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the Besshi {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жЬИ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, the term "month" here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Daisetsu|ja|е§ІйЫ™|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|е∞ПеѓТ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Day of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЧ•)==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йБЄжЧ•|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for Besshi is as follows.
===Selected Day (йБЄжЧ•)===
Besshi day is the 7th (final) day of the {{ill|Hando|ja|зКѓеЬЯ|lt=Hando|lt_ja=е§ІеЬЯ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} period.


