==Month of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЬИ)==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Kou|ja|зФ≤|1=Kinoe (зФ≤)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (зФ≤)|qq=}} and {{ill|Ki|ja|еЈ±|1=Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November|qq=}} is designated as the Besshi {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}}. However, the term "month" here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Daisetsu|ja|е§ІйЫ™|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daisetsu|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|е∞ПеѓТ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Cold|qq=}}) as applicable.

==Day of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЧ•)==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йБЄжЧ•|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for Besshi is as follows.
===Selected Day (йБЄжЧ•)===
Besshi day is the 7th (final) day of the {{ill|Hando|ja|зКѓеЬЯ|lt=Hando|lt_ja=е§ІеЬЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=}} period.

