==Month of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЬИ)== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Kou|ja|зФ≤|1=Kinoe (зФ≤)|lt=Kinoe (зФ≤)|2=ja|3=зФ≤|4=zh|5=зФ≤|1=Kinoe (зФ≤)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (зФ≤)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (зФ≤)|qq=}} and {{ill|Ki|ja|еЈ±|1=Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|lt=Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|2=ja|3=еЈ±|4=zh|5=еЈ±|1=Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (еЈ±)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:November|November]] is designated as the Besshi [[:en:Month|Month]]. However, the term "month" here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from [[:en:Daxue (solar term)|Daisetsu]] until the day before [[:en:Xiaohan|Lesser Cold]]) as applicable.
==Day of Besshi (дЄЩе≠РгБЃжЧ•)== The {{ill|selected day|ja|йБЄжЧ•|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for Besshi is as follows. ===Selected Day (йБЄжЧ•)=== Besshi day is the 7th (final) day of the {{ill|Hando|ja|зКѓеЬЯ|lt=Hando|lt_ja=е§ІеЬЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=}} period.
